label: Parent Record; Atlas and farmers' directory of Winona County, Minnesota, 1914

metadata.label: Description
metadata.value: Atlas and farmers' directory of Winona County, Minnesota, containing plats of all townships with owners names, also maps of the state and the United States, with an outline map of the county showing the location of townships, villages, roads, schools, churches, railroads, streams, etc.
